title: Architecture in the Real World - The Work of Hok (Art).pdf
description:
Architecture in the Real World - The Work of Hok
Harry N. Abrams | 1985 | ISBN: 0810918226 | English | 240 pages | PDF | 34.2 MB


A close look behind the facade of the profession of architecture: the day to day life of a practice, the design process, production techniques, marketing of architectural services, and, uniquely, the complexities of one architectural firm's own finances. 100 full color illustrations, 120 duotone illustrations, 50 line drawings
